c: 7
v: 44
t: "And the inhabitants of the garden will call out to the inhabitants of the fire (saying) that, \"We have found that which our Fosterer promised us, to be true, so have you (too) found that which your Fosterer promised you, to be true?\" They will say, \"Yes.\" Then an announcer will announce among them that: \"Curse of Allah is on the unjust"